cscie97.asn4.housemate.entitlement

Class Resource

  • java.lang.Object
    • cscie97.asn4.housemate.entitlement.Item
      • cscie97.asn4.housemate.entitlement.Resource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IEntitlementVisitable

    public class Resource
extends Item
implements IEntitlementVisitable
    Resources represent the major functional areas of the House Mate Service, which now includes the EntitlementServiceAPI, HouseMateControllerServiceAPI, and HouseMateModelServiceAPI. Primarily marker classes for logical groupings of child Permissions, Resources don't currently exhibit much behavior.
    See Also:
    Permission, IEntitlementServiceAPI
